{"tid":1250384,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"才下眉頭 卻上心頭","createTime":"2019-06-22T05:10:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-22T09:46:55.000Z","uid":63064,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8ce077dcd474d0848567d10680b821e351b8b91","tid":1250384,"uid":63064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:10:23.000Z","msg":"分開左都一段時間 都仲係無變過 完全忘記唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人話忘記一個人最好既方法就係開始另一段新感情 我唔係冇試過 仲識左好多人 但每當自己叫做有啲好感嘅時候就好似即刻開左保護罩咁 明明好好傾我都係突然好冷淡 唔想當人係水泡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以為忙忙下就會忘記 結果心裡面只係不停諗住佢<br />\n每日朝早扮好開心 夜晚就叫春叫到三四點 究竟可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8bf9cf7cb881b93dfc6dfab5e6b8392b967630b","tid":1250384,"uid":244569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"唔好諗住自己當人地係水泡先<br />\n因為你有呢個諗頭就好容易真係成真<br />\n慢慢黎當識朋友先啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>加油啊</strong>"},{"pid":"bcf91731bf62891c1e69da448dd9427953c59702","tid":1250384,"uid":63064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8bf9cf7cb881b93dfc6dfab5e6b8392b967630b","tid":1250384,"uid":244569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"唔好諗住自己當人地係水泡先<br />\n因為你有呢個諗頭就好容易真係成真<br />\n慢慢黎當識朋友先啦ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong>加油啊</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-22T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗 當住朋友先 <br />\n不過最慘去到邊我都會諗起個ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66b5f0eaa90ab94d3db776bc5a101b4c4146251d","tid":1250384,"uid":230054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"